    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/b9c79914279b9c20ff08d0cf1da848fe.avif?t=1758953155\" width=600 height=140 /></span><br>准备在《Bears In Space》中释放你内心的野熊吧！这款夸张的枪战弹雨FPS游戏一定会让你兴奋到怒吼！你会化身为麦克斯韦·阿托姆斯——一名退休的太空宇航员，现在则是一名太空流浪者——一头扎进成群的嗜油机器人之中。他的DNA已与“熊女”熊塔娜融合了。<br>踏上一场荒诞不经、超凡脱俗的冒险之旅：你将闯过有趣而各异的地点，从荒原到太空嘉年华，再到古老隐秘的神庙等等，只为寻找那条返回地球的路。如果时间来得及，还要拯救你的船员。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快节奏的混乱</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/1ec034f4520c3475bb8485cda63066cd.poster.avif?t=1758953155\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/1ec034f4520c3475bb8485cda63066cd.webm?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/1ec034f4520c3475bb8485cda63066cd.mp4?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《Bears In Space》提供的是不间断的高能游戏节奏。使用各种不像话的武器和小工具，在一波波凶猛的机器人中杀出一条血路吧。你可以二段跳、冲刺以及闪避敌人的攻击：沿袭了老式射击游戏的优良传统。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >熊罴之力</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/6d97af783b26c5519ae69324d8f5afdd.poster.avif?t=1758953155\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/6d97af783b26c5519ae69324d8f5afdd.webm?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/6d97af783b26c5519ae69324d8f5afdd.mp4?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>吃下神出鬼没的蜜罐，释放你的熊熊怒火，变身成熊！  <br>利用你独特的DNA融合优势，用你强大的熊罴之力和精湛的古代熊功夫知识以及传说中的熊之拳，将机器人敌人碎尸万段吧。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级武器库</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/5066081b47f2097b2b99a884b0ea38ae.poster.avif?t=1758953155\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/5066081b47f2097b2b99a884b0ea38ae.webm?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/5066081b47f2097b2b99a884b0ea38ae.mp4?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>完成挑战、打碎战利品箱并购买枪支，有超过25种武器供你选择！<br>大多数武器都能升级，每次击杀都会获得当前装备武器的经验值，随后武器就会进化到下一个等级！所以，赶快行动起来，让激光飞起来吧！<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的游戏玩法</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/013a85507a366767e8a91cf5e94a55f8.poster.avif?t=1758953155\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/013a85507a366767e8a91cf5e94a55f8.webm?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309620/extras/013a85507a366767e8a91cf5e94a55f8.mp4?t=1758953155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>超越普通FPS的体验，在每个关卡中探索支线故事、秘密和收藏品吧！<br>你可以学习如何烘焙蛋糕、调查犯罪现场、与摇滚歌神对战、玩一局篮块，甚至还能抓鬼！与此同时，你还会遇到一群丰富多彩的人物，他们每个人都有自己的怪癖和故事。<br>完成这些刺激的可选奇遇能带来丰厚的战利品奖励，这一点在你为下一件武器攒钱的时候就变得尤为重要了！<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择难度，按自己的方式玩游戏！</h2></strong><br>你可以使用独立的滑块来调节受到和打出的伤害量。你还可以使用我们的“平台助手”模式，使游戏中的所有平台部分都更容易征服！非常适合儿童或刚接触FPS类型游戏的玩家！<br>无论你是想感受怀旧冲击的资深玩家，还是想体验充满乐趣的冒险的休闲玩家，《Bears in Space》都将为你带来一段欢乐、荒诞、充满动作的时光。准备好射击和欢笑，然后在这款独一无二的弹雨FPS中释放内心的野熊，进行一场真正的超凡冒险吧！",
